item.title: Pvpscapez need devolopers!
item.dc:creator: @Team_Rocket Team_Rocket
item.description:
@Team_Rocket wrote:

drubrkletern:

You should try and add some custom content yourself first, it looks like a generic pi server, not too many people may want to help you with it in this state

This, and also, your

filling out thing

is called a Developer Application. It’s way too short and very poorly done, as is this Server Development Thread.

You’re going to need to bring something serious to the table if you’re wanting to attract serious Developers.

P.S. Posting pictures of incorrect Models and Tutorial Interfaces isn’t the type of Media you should be posting.
